text:
Hi,
I would like tos show recent 3 posts from a specific tag from the blog.

I tried this code:
```{% set pop_posts = blog_popular_posts('default', 5, 'marketing-tips') %}
{% for pop_post in pop_posts %}
    &lt;div class="post-title"&gt;{{ pop_post.name }}&lt;/div&gt;
{% endfor %}```
from here: <https://designers.HubSpot.com/docs/hubl/functions#blog-recent-topic-posts> but with this code I am unable to show feature image and permalink of that post.
